{"tid":1487804,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我係支共，你玩人鏈我好開心！因為示威者將會一鋪清袋！","createTime":"2019-08-19T12:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T17:30:28.000Z","uid":75448,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"71f5d7ae820dc2aedfaf0444e5cd1588da86cef6","tid":1487804,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:03:41.000Z","msg":"我係中共見你地班傻鳩玩人鏈就好撚開心成班人企定定畀人影大頭，派人跟住條人鏈360度影哂你地大頭做人臉識別易過借火。<br />\n<br />\n你地結人鏈雙手拖住旁邊果個人，到時搵人除你口罩呀帽呀都仲得。都未講拖住隻手搵人打你都冇手擋，成班人打靶咁任鬧任潑屎尿都仲得，諗起都興奮。<br />\n<br />\n只要開住架車放兩三個人望住條街影就收到哂所有示威者個樣的資料，唔洗搞事你地就仆街，如果遇武力反抗仲可以扮多似記者畀人打的戲碼。<br />\n<br />\n諗起到想你地快啲搞人鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"937f265c70b50b4aaa36db572175f7572966db89","tid":1487804,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:07:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e2c42e7d98480f5200468a4665c469cbd943d66","tid":1487804,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:12:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0da13ee1a64aecf1ebdc48efacb1d2fa2be7bebc","tid":1487804,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:15:03.000Z","msg":"一鋪清袋冇人理"},{"pid":"c2bea91cb82f8572c9c94cb831ed3515fde98a6f","tid":1487804,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:21:33.000Z","msg":"推到熱門"},{"pid":"a744bf68847c113b589d93be4feadf71a64db5c3","tid":1487804,"uid":248290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:56:19.000Z","msg":"有道理&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74edce166316f6ad9922e3571ab9c68bd9a4089a","tid":1487804,"uid":152455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:27:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb6c3e8eb250eebc3df05b6b476ccdeff0d6ebf3","tid":1487804,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86f12681a07